headline: Lam Research initiated at ‘outperform’ by Oppenheimer on AI, NAND upgrades
summary: Investing.com -- Oppenheimer initiated coverage on Lam Research Corp (NASDAQ:LRCX) with an Outperform rating and a price target of $95 given the semiconductor equipment maker’s dominant position in etch technology and its growth potential from NAND upgrades and AI-related demand.
